{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十八回\"祖孙\"。李寻欢离开神秘老人后心境萧索，来到山村\"停车爱醉枫林晚\"酒铺。他回忆孙驼子的隐忍、孙小红的情意以及阿飞的孤独倔强。在酒铺中，李寻欢遇见上官飞焦急等待，随后两顶绿泥小轿到来。红衣小姑娘接走上官飞，李寻欢尾随至山坡枫林深处的小楼。他发现林仙儿与上官飞在轿中亲热，确认林仙儿在此。李寻欢等待上官飞离去后进入小楼，却只见白发老太婆和自称周姑娘的小姑娘，声称从未有人来过。林仙儿与上官飞竟凭空消失。李寻欢无奈只取走一瓶酒离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你留在这里，只有增加她的烦恼和痛苦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她虽然像是天上的仙子，却专门带男人下地狱！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "红衣小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "text": "公子久候了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "上官飞",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "红衣小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "text": "停车爱醉枫林晚，娇靥红于二月花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "上官飞",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "她呢？她不能来？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "红衣小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "text": "公子且莫心焦，请随我来……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "text": "小飞，不要这样……在这里不可以……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "上官飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我简直等不及了……你知不知道我多想你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "text": "原来你也和别的男人一样，想我，就是为了要欺负我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "上官飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "对，我就是要欺负，因为我知道你喜欢被男人欺负，是不是……是不是……是不是？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_fei",
      "text": "是是是，你欺负我吧……欺负我吧……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来轿子里有两个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你……你是谁？到这里来干什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "我来找个老朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "老朋友？谁是你的老朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "她看到我时，一定会认得的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这里没有你的老朋友，这里只有我和我孙女两个人。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "奶奶这人是强盗么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "text": "你看我像不像强盗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你若不是强盗，为什么三更半夜闯到人家里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "text": "我是来找林姑娘的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这里没有林姑娘，只有位周姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "text": "周姑娘在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我姓周，周姑娘就是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但我却不认得你，你为何来找我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "text": "我找的是位大姑娘，不是小姑娘。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这里没有大姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "text": "这里刚刚没有人来过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "有人来过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我和我奶奶，我们刚从镇上回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这里只有两个人，小的是我，大的是我奶奶，但她也早就不是'姑娘'了，你总不会是找她吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "除了我和我奶奶外，这里既没有人来过，也没有人出去，你若是看到别人，一定是见着鬼了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我们祖孙都是可怜人，这里也没有什么值钱的东西，大爷你无论看上了什么，只管拿走就是。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来这人并不是强盗，只不过是个酒鬼而已。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 413
    }
